thread.title: BRIEF-XiAn Qujiang Cultural Tourism sees FY 2017 net profit up 15 pct to 35 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-XiAn Qujiang Cultural Tourism sees FY 2017 net profit up 15 pct to 35 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - xian qujiang cultural tourism co ltd

text:
Feb 1(Reuters) - XiAn Qujiang Cultural Tourism Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 15 percent to 35 percent, or to increase by 8 million yuan to 19 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 53.4 million yuan
* The reason for the forecast is improved performance of subsidiaries Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/HhwEaX Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
